code: @Override public void setBeanClassLoader(ClassLoader classLoader) {     this.classLoader = classLoader. }

@Bean(destroyMethod = "shutdown") public EmbeddedDatabase dataSource(DataSourceProperties properties) {     return new EmbeddedDatabaseBuilder().setType(EmbeddedDatabaseConnection.get(this.classLoader).getType()).setName(properties.determineDatabaseName()).build(). }
